Privacy Policy for Data Structure Visualization Application

This Privacy Policy describes how the Data Structure Visualization Application (the “Application”) collects, uses, shares, and protects the personal information of its users. By using the Application, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy. If you do not agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy, you must not use the Application.

Collection of Personal Information: The Application may collect personal information from you, including but not limited to your name, email address, gender, age, and any other information you choose to provide through the Application’s login page or through your use of the Application.

Use of Personal Information: The Application may use your personal information to provide you with access to the Application and its features, to improve the Application, to contact you with updates and promotional offers, and for other purposes as described in this Privacy Policy.

Sharing of Personal Information: The Application may share your personal information with third-party service providers for the purpose of operating the Application, providing customer support, and conducting analytics. These third-party service providers are bound by confidentiality obligations and may only use your personal information as necessary to perform their functions and not for any other purposes.

Storage and Protection of Personal Information: The Application takes reasonable precautions to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure. However, no internet-based platform can be 100% secure, and the Application cannot guarantee the security of your personal information.

Data Retention: The Application will retain your personal information for as long as your account is active or as needed to provide you with the Application’s services. The Application will retain and use your personal information as necessary to comply with legal obligations, resolve disputes, and enforce its agreements.

Changes to Privacy Policy: The Application may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in its practices or applicable laws. If the Application makes any material changes, it will notify you by email or through a notice on the Application. Your continued use of the Application after any such changes constitutes your acceptance of the new Privacy Policy.

Contact Information: If you have any questions or concerns about the Application’s Privacy Policy, please contact the Application at [insert contact information].
